<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA95">
<l>avaḷōr kulamaṅkai pākat takalā</l>
<l>ḷāvaḷōr calamakaḷu mītē - tavaḷanī</l>
<l>ṟeṉpaṇivī reṉṟum pirintaṟiyī rīṅkivaru</l>
<l>ḷaṉpaṇiyār collumiṉiṅ kār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She who will not depart from [her] share [in you], she is a girl of family.</l>
<l>This, this one is a water woman. You adorned with</l>
<l>white ashes [and] bones, who will never separate [from them], among these here</l>
<l>who is the one here close by love, speak?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
